      <title>通胀缓慢放缓将支持美联储降息谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/fed-rate-cuts-glacial-inflation-slowdown-set-to-back-central-bank-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继就业数据出奇强劲之后，未来一周美国消费者价格数据预计将显示潜在通胀大幅放缓，这解释了美联储在降息方面采取的谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/fed-rate-cuts-glacial-inflation-slowdown-set-to-back-central-bank-caution</guid>
